| location       = 2-1-1 Miyamoto-chō, Kiryu, Gunma Prefecture, Japan
| deity          = {{nihongo|Ōmononushi Kushi-mika-tama-no-Mikoto|大物主櫛甕玉命}}<br>{{nihongo|Takehayasusanoo-no-Mikoto|武速須佐之男命}}
| established    = During the reign of Emperor Sujin
| former_rank    = {{nihongo|Shikinaisha (minor)|式内社（小）}}, {{nihongo|Gōsha (郷社)|郷社}}
| festivals      = November 19–20 (Kiryu Ebisu Festival)
